Text: YPO Mardi Gras Fly Away Greetings YPOers Last chance for those of you who have not signed up for this upcoming YPO Fly Away of a lifetime In case you forgot what your missing here is a recap of events Dinner at Palace Cafe Brunch at Commanders Palace Ride on the Krewe of Orpheus float in full costume Party at Krewe of Orpheus Ball and lots of more surprises Cost per rider is per person Spouses are welcome to ride too You have until July st to respond and then it is open to WPOers The dates again are February Please contact KayLa Hughes at ext to sign up Les Bon Temps Rouler Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday April PM To Cc
